long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Woodpecker Prospects offers a seamless transition from prospecting to outreach. Our Chrome Extension is meticulously crafted to elevate your prospecting journey on LinkedIn and Sales Navigator. It empowers users to efficiently gather, organize, and manage prospect data from LinkedIn profiles, making lead generation a breeze.

Join the trust of over 13,000 professionals who rely on Woodpecker. As a proud member of the Woodpecker.co family, it complements our suite, including Cold Email, Sales Assistant, and Agency, making it an indispensable tool for cold emailing and lead generation. 

Streamline your process with Woodpecker Prospects today.
